-- Lanxess CFO Says on Course to Reach 2015 Profit Goal, BZ Reports
-- B y   A n n e t t e   W e i s b a c h
-- 2012-06-22T17:28:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-22/lanxess-cfo-says-on-course-to-reach-2015-profit-goal-bz-reports.html
Lanxess AG (LXS)  is on course to reach its
operating profit goal of 1.4 billion euros ($1.8 billion) in
2015, according to a report in Boersenzeitung, which cited an
interview with Chief Financial Officer Bernhard Duettmann.  To meet the goal, the company needs to invest in growth
projects limiting the room for higher dividends, the paper said,
citing Duettmann.  To contact the reporter on this story:
